README for argyllcms

POST-INSTALL
----
  Please add your argyllcms user to scanner group!

NOTES
----
  * The documentaion is only available as html, you will find it in
    /usr/share/argyllcms/doc
  * Color charts located in /usr/share/argyllcms/ref
  * Experimental ColorHug support is compiled in, but is disabled unless the
    environment variable "ENABLE_COLORHUG" is set.
